{"tid":1168724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少年爬列車頂自拍示愛　女友目睹他瞬間自爆慘死","createTime":"2019-05-24T01:22:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T00:27:28.000Z","uid":130626,"like":307,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"46dcd941f46652f99f96c19ef4d91254587f87c3","tid":1168724,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:22:43.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯卡拉蘇克(Karasuk)一名13歲少年柯洛謝夫(Oleg Khoroshaev)，日前爬上一輛列車車頂自拍，想要拍下「讓女友驚豔的照片」來示愛，沒想到柯洛謝夫一爬上車頂，就在女友面前被27500伏特電纜電擊，瞬間自爆，女友眼睜睜看著他變成一團火球。<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，有女性目擊者指出，當時她看到一群少年與女孩在鐵軌附近亂晃，據悉這處車站是貨運列車的主要車站。當時柯洛謝夫爬上其中一輛列車車頂，其他男孩也想要跟著爬上去，並問柯洛謝夫說：「你覺得怎麼樣？」但柯洛謝夫還來不及回答，就馬上被高壓電電擊，瞬間「自爆」變成一團火球，全身嚴重燒傷。女目擊者說，少年的狀況非常悽慘，可以聽到他的尖叫哀號，「就連成年男子看他都會覺得心痛」。<br />\n隨後少年被送醫，但治療3天後仍傷重不治身亡。報導指出，少年為了自拍，想拍下最厲害的照片討女友歡心，沒想到卻被女友目睹慘狀。但有一名少年的朋友說，少年當時沒有要自拍，但是帶著手機爬列車車頂。<br />\n近日不止這起案件，在白俄羅斯明斯克地區，也發生有一名14歲少年帶頭，和朋友一起挑戰爬列車車頂，並在現場自拍 (詳見影片)。這名少年和朋友，同樣也被高壓電纜瞬間電擊爆炸，少年嚴重傷燒、不治身亡，而朋友則是幸運地僅受傷，無生命危險。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190524/640_854ab0bf694241c4a1dd4366629cad05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190524%2F640_854ab0bf694241c4a1dd4366629cad05.jpg&h=c0d38b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n少年柯洛謝夫爬列車頂自拍示愛，女友目睹他瞬間自爆慘死，車頂還遺留爆炸痕跡。翻自《太陽報》<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190524/640_d6474eb2dafb88f026ded5d96ea5bae6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190524%2F640_d6474eb2dafb88f026ded5d96ea5bae6.jpg&h=1ba639ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n柯洛謝夫一爬上車頂，就在女友面前被27500伏特電纜電擊，瞬間自爆。翻自《太陽報》<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190524/640_79f896eb39ea2f4b7ef3227608b649b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190524%2F640_79f896eb39ea2f4b7ef3227608b649b2.jpg&h=5d20e872&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n柯洛謝夫和女友的合影。翻自《太陽報》<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190524/1572199/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190524%2F1572199%2F&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhFQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=1f41d84e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190524%2F1572199%2F&h=97a753ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190524/1572199/</a>"},{"pid":"2223bfbd56016f72013c6ef8a231af3914ce2b8e","tid":1168724,"uid":181283,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:27:20.000Z","msg":"施旖婕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2261c8dfb1b4c03a118a26935e29bd0d0d30fd92","tid":1168724,"uid":127202,"like":1073,"dislike":5,"score":1068,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:29:42.000Z","msg":"13歲，靚靚仔仔又有女<br />\n可惜弱智"},{"pid":"071da114db98bf4c7504506c390e57d84391873e","tid":1168724,"uid":61545,"like":104,"dislike":4,"score":100,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:31:54.000Z","msg":"咁都頂到3日先死"},{"pid":"f4beac853a0ab95cadece9ad53f18a13bfc91148","tid":1168724,"uid":141151,"like":336,"dislike":4,"score":332,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:36:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>愛得轟裂</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3166061c25d2bee9e293888144dd03d1867ca48c","tid":1168724,"uid":192581,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:36:28.000Z","msg":"戰鬥民族精神永存！"},{"pid":"92546900c74e9d96b9c2ec82474936d8aaf08530","tid":1168724,"uid":228532,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T01:39:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9fa247ff0418d20bd8b01ff05ca001c30492a1c7","tid":1168724,"uid":63870